* Fix CI matrix includes
* Fix warning 37 in BatConcreteQueue on OCaml < 4.08

* Disable unattached documentation comment warnings on old OCaml versions
* Only build @install in dune CI

* Add bigarray dependency in dune
* Exclude versioned BatConcreteQueues in dune
